"Academic Transcript" actually means something different for advisors. I checked your Academic Transcript and the title is there for EE 127. On CalCentral, I believe you are viewing on "My Academics" and the title is missing. This is a confusing thing that the system is sometimes doing when there is no grade yet for the course. I would sit tight for now and wait for the grade to be posted. If the title is still not there after you get your grade, then you can send in a helpticket.
